Description
-----------

The mask\_left keywork only allows sound from the shader to be outbut through the front left surround sound speaker in a 5.1 setup, or the left speaker in the 2 channel (stereo) setup.

Usage
-----

`mask_left`

Example
-------

`ship_engine_rumble`
`{`
`   mindistance 100`
`   maxdistance 1000`
`   volume 10`
`   looping`
`   mask_left`
`   shakes .1`
`   sound/last_stand/loop_rumble_left_b.wav`
`}`

